@right
on-arrival: {!
if (Q.ideology && Q.ideology != "reformist") {
    Q.changed = 1;
}
!}
go-to: changed if changed = 1
on-departure: ideology = "right"; right_strength += 10; right_dissent -= 5; gdvp_relation += 5; sdapo_relation -= 5

The right wing text 👍 

@changed
on-arrival: right_dissent += 5; center_dissent += 5; labor_dissent += 5; clerical_dissent += 5

We have changed ideologies. Many in the party feel unmoored.
